---
import ApplicationLayout from '../layouts/ApplicationLayout.astro';

const productJsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Product",
  "name": "Alfa Laval WHPX 513 Self-Cleaning, Diesel Fuel Oil Centrifuge",
  "description": "Alfa Laval WHPX-513 Partial Discharge centrifuge finds multiple uses for fuel, lube oil, waste oil, and other 3-phase, fluid purification applications.",
  "url": "https://dolphincentrifuge.com/alfa-laval-whpx-513/"
};

const jsonLd = [productJsonLd];

const toc = [
  { id: 'overview', label: 'Overview' },
  { id: 'application', label: 'Application' },
  { id: 'whpx-513-specifications', label: 'WHPX 513 Specifications' },
  { id: 'fopx-613', label: 'FOPX 613 Partial-Discharge Centrifuge' },
  { id: 'fopx-613-specifications', label: 'FOPX 613 Specifications' },
  { id: 'mopx-213', label: 'MOPX 213 Total-Discharge Centrifuge' },
  { id: 'mopx-213-specifications', label: 'MOPX 213 Specifications' },
  { id: 'WHPX-513-Gallery', label: 'WHPX 513 Centrifuge Modules Gallery' },
];

const relatedApplications = [
  { label: 'Diesel Fuel Centrifuge', href: '/diesel-fuel-purifier/' },
  { label: 'Fuel Oil Centrifuge', href: '/fuel-oil-centrifuge/' },
  { label: 'Waste Oil Centrifuge', href: '/waste-oil-centrifuge/' },
  { label: 'Lube Oil Centrifuge', href: '/lube-oil-centrifuge/' },
  { label: 'Machine Coolant Centrifuge', href: '/machine-coolant-centrifuge/' },
];
---

<ApplicationLayout
  title="Alfa Laval WHPX 513 Self-Cleaning, Diesel Fuel Oil Centrifuge"
  description="Alfa Laval WHPX-513 Partial Discharge centrifuge finds multiple uses for fuel, lube oil, waste oil, and other 3-phase, fluid purification applications."
  category="products"
  categoryLabel="Products"
  heroImage="/images/alfa-laval-whpx-513/Alfa-Laval-WHPX513-Centrifuge-Skid-600.webp"
  heroImageAlt="Alfa Laval WHPX513 Centrifuge Skid"
  canonicalUrl="https://dolphincentrifuge.com/alfa-laval-whpx-513/"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  toc={toc}
  relatedApplications={relatedApplications}
>

  <h3 id="overview">Overview</h3>

  <p>The Alfa Laval WHPX 513 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc-stack centrifuge</a> built for the three-phase separation of mixed fluids and sludge.</p>

  <p>With a 15 HP Motor, the WHPX 513 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 4,150 and can process 72 GPM of Diesel Fuel.</p>

  <h3 id="application">Application</h3>

  <p>The Alfa Laval WHPX 513 Centrifuge is widely used in marine and industrial applications. Some of these applications are:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong><a href="/diesel-fuel-purifier/">Diesel Fuel</a></strong></li>
    <li><a href="/black-diesel-centrifuge/"><strong>Black Diesel</strong></a></li>
    <li><strong><a href="/fuel-oil-centrifuge/">Intermediate and Heavy Fuel Oils (IFO, HFO)</a></strong></li>
    <li><strong><a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/">Waste Oil</a></strong></li>
    <li><strong><a href="/machine-coolant-centrifuge/">Industrial Fluids &amp; Machining Coolants</a></strong></li>
    <li><strong><a href="/lube-oil-centrifuge/">Lubricating Oils</a></strong>.</li>
  </ul>

  <figure>
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-whpx-513/Alfa-Laval-WHPX513-Centrifuge-Skid-600.webp"
      alt="Alfa Laval WHPX513 Centrifuge Skid"
      width="600"
      height="450"
      loading="lazy"
      class="img-cap-600"
    />
    <figcaption>Alfa Laval WHPX 513 Centrifuge System with Feed Pump, Sludge Tank</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <h3 id="whpx-513-specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto border border-gray-100 rounded-xl">
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Model Type</td><td>Alfa Laval WHPX 513 TGD 24-60</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rated Capacity</td><td>72 GPM on 13 cSt Diesel Fuel</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sludge Space</td><td>3.87 Gallons</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Motor HP:</td><td>15 HP</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Voltages:</td><td>230 / 460 V</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2 id="fopx-613">Alfa Laval FOPX 613 TFD Partial-Discharge Disc-Stack Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The Alfa Laval FOPX 613 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning disc-stack centrifuge specially built for the three-phase separation of fuel oils, such as <a href="/fuel-oil-centrifuge/">heavy fuel oil</a> (HFO). The <strong>FO </strong>in FOPX stands for <strong>F</strong>uel <strong>O</strong>il.</p>

  <p>With a 15 HP Motor, the FOPX 613 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 4,100 and can process 30 GPM of ISO 380 cSt Heavy Fuel Oil.</p>

  <figure>
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-whpx-513/Alfa-Laval-FOPX613-HFO-Centrifuge-System.webp"
