  </div>

  <h2 id="mopx-213">Alfa Laval MOPX 213 TGT Total-Discharge Disc-Stack Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The Alfa Laval MOPX 213 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning disc-stack centrifuge designed for the three-phase separation of <a href="/fuel-oil-centrifuge/">fuel oil</a>, <a href="/hydraulic-oil-centrifuge/">hydraulic oil</a>, <a href="/cutting-oil-centrifuge/">cutting oil</a>, and other mineral oil and fuel.</p>

  <p>With a 15 HP Motor, the MOPX 213 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 4,150 and can process 40 GPM of Used Engine Oil at 180 F.</p>

  <figure>
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-whpx-513/waste-motor-oil-centrifuge-system.webp"
      alt="Waste Motor Oil Centrifuge System"
      width="600"
      height="450"
      loading="lazy"
      class="img-cap-600"
    />
    <figcaption>Waste Motor Oil Centrifuge System. Includes clean oil tank, pumps, sludge handling system heater, and PLC controls.</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <h3 id="mopx-213-specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto border border-gray-100 rounded-xl">
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Model Type</td><td>Alfa Laval MOPX 213 TGT 20-60</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rated Capacity</td><td>42 GPM on Used Motor Oil @ 180 F</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sludge Space</td><td>3.61 Gallons</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Motor HP:</td><td>15 HP</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Voltages:</td><td>230 / 460 V</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

